-----------------

Gradle Enterprise tasks
-----------------------
buildScanPublishPrevious - Publishes the data captured by the last build.
provisionGradleEnterpriseAccessKey - Provisions a new access key for this build environment.

Help tasks
----------

tasks - Displays the tasks runnable from root project 'spring-boot-build' (some of the displayed tasks may belong to subprojects).
spring-boot-project:tasks - Displays the tasks runnable from project ':spring-boot-project' (some of the displayed tasks may belong to subprojects).

Plugin development tasks
------------------------
spring-boot-project:spring-boot-tools:spring-boot-gradle-plugin:pluginDescriptors - Generates plugin descriptors from plugin declarations.
spring-boot-project:spring-boot-tools:spring-boot-gradle-plugin:pluginUnderTestMetadata - Generates the metadata for plugin functional tests.
spring-boot-project:spring-boot-tools:spring-boot-gradle-plugin:validatePlugins - Validates the plugin by checking parameter annotations on task and artifact transform types etc.
